snippet.title: Mathness Gameplay Trailer (2023)
snippet.description:
Mathness is a story-driven adventure puzzle game with a mysterious world and a touch of mathematics. Explore the interconnected world of Delearnia. Make your way through the obstacles and boss battles by collecting new magical skills and unlocking new tools. Become the Mathemagician! 

For more information: https://www.mathness.fi/
